If you are working for the ONS and are using (or planning to use) the design system, you can ask a question or make a suggestion by getting in touch with the team and our community of collaborators.

## GitHub
If you have any problems using the design system, you can add a comment using the GitHub discussions link at the end of every pattern, component or style page, or find the relevant one on {{
    onsExternalLink({
        "url": "https://github.com/ONSdigital/design-system/discussions",
        "linkText": "GitHub discussions"
    })
}}

To get notifications about new releases you can {{
    onsExternalLink({
        "url": "https://github.com/ONSdigital/design-system/releases",
        "linkText": "watch the design system repository on GitHub"
    })
}}

## Slack
